title.narrative: Old Component - DFID Humanitarian and Emergency Operations Support Service

description.narrative: This activity (Old Component - DFID Humanitarian and Emergency Operations Support Service) is a component of DFID Humanitarian and Emergency Operations Support Service reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Humanitarian assistance' and a budget of £11,609,176. This component benefits Developing countries, unspecified, and works in the following sector(s): Material relief assistance and services . , with the following implementing partners: Crown Agents Limited. The start date is 01-05-2012 and the end date is 30-04-2017.
